  <?dbhtml filename="fixesproto.html"?>

  <title>fixesproto-&fixesproto-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      This extension makes changes to many areas of the protocol to resolve
      issues raised by application interaction with core protocol mechanisms
      that cannot be adequately worked around on the client side of the wire.
    </para>

